<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whenever-conj">whenever <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wen'evə(r)/    美 /wen'evər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>每当：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Whenever we met with difficulties, they came to help us. 
每当我们遇到困难的时候，他们都会来帮忙。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>无论何时：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We try to help <strong>whenever possible</strong>.
只要有可能我们都会尽量帮忙。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When I was a child, I could watch TV whenever I wanted to.
我小的时候，无论什么时候想看电视都能看。</p><footer>2013 江西</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong> I have to give a speech, I get extremely nervous before I start.  （2013 山东）<br />
A.Whatever<br />
B.Whenever<br />
C.Whoever<br />
D.However  </li>
<li>The map is one of the best tools a man has <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ he goes to a new place.  （2012 上海）<br />
A.whenever<br />
B.whatever<br />
C.wherever<br />
D.however  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. B  2. A  </p></div>